public class SelectableDockHeader
    
extends javax.swing.JPanel
    
implements SelectableHeader

A header for a dock that can be selected.

It contains a label with the names of the dockables in the dock.

Author:
Heidi Rakels.

SelectableDockHeader

public SelectableDockHeader(Dock dock,
                            int position)

Constructs a small header for a dock that can be selected.

The title of the dock is set in the header.

Parameters:
dock - The dock of the header.
position - The position of the header. Possible values are constants defined by the class Position, i.e.:
  • Position.LEFT,
  • Position.RIGHT,
  • Position.TOP,
  • Position.BOTTOM.
